quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  77,1,Ndayidde empewo ekunta mu ngeri y'okugoberegana
  77,2,Era ndayidde kibuyaga akunta mu ngeri ey'amaanyi eyakabi
  77,3,Era ndayidde Malayika ezitambuza ebire olutambuza (olwokutonyesa enkuba)
  77,4,Era ndayidde Malayika ezikka okuva ewa Katonda nga zireeta ebyawula wakati w'amazima n'obulimba
  77,5,Era ndayidde Malayika ezireeta ebitabo n'obubaka eri ba Nabbi ba Katonda nga byakujjukiza
  77,6,Mu ngeri yokuba nti bijjawo ebyokwekwaasa oba nga byakutiisa
  77,7,Mazima bye mulaganyisibwa ebikwata ku lunaku lw'enkomerero n'okusasulwa bya kubaawo
  77,8,Emunyeenye lweziriggibwawo (newataba kitangaala kyaazo)
  77,9,Era eggulu bweririwumulwa (nerirabika nga emiryango)
  77,10,Era ensozi bwezirimerengulwa
  77,11,Era ababaka b'a Katonda bwebaliweebwa akadde k'okuwa obujulizi kwabo bebaatumwamu
  77,12,(Ebintu ebyo ebyentiisa) biribaawo ddi
  77,13,Bigenda kubaawo ku lunaku olwokusalawo n'okulamula wakati w'ebitonde
  77,14,Abaffe omanyi olunaku lw'okusalawo kyekki
  77,15,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kw'abo abalulimbisa
  77,16,Abaffe tetwazikiriza ababasokawo
  77,17,Netubagoberezaako abalala
  77,18,Bwetutyo nno bwetukola mu kubonereza abonoonyi
  77,19,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,20,Abaffe tetwabakola nga tubajja mu mazzi aganyomebwa
  77,21,Netugateeka mukifo ekigakuuma
  77,22,Okutuusa ebbanga eggere erimanyiddwa
  77,23,Bwetutyo nno bwetwateekateeka okutondebwa kwabwe tuli bateesiteesi abasinga obulungi
  77,24,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,25,Abaffe ensi tetwagikola nga ekungaanya
  77,26,Abalamu n'abafu (bonna ngabali muyo)
  77,27,Netugiteekamu e nsozi eziginyweza entumbiivu ne tubawa amazzi amalungi
  77,28,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,29,Ku lunaku lw'enkomerero abakafiiri baliragirwa nti mugende eri ebyo bye mwali mulimbisa
  77,30,Mugende eri ekisiikirize ekyomuliro ngakirimu ebitundu bisatu
  77,31,Wabula tebaliba na kibasiikiriza wadde e kibataasa nnimi z'amuliro
  77,32,Mazima omuliro ogwo gukasuka ebitawuliro nga biringa ebizimbe ebigulumivu
  77,33,Ebitawuliro ebyo nga biringa engamiya ez'akyenvu
  77,34,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,35,Olwo lunaku lwebatagenda kwogera
  77,36,Wadde okukkirizibwa okwetonda
  77,37,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,38,Luno lwe lunaku lw'okulamula tubakunganyizza mwenna n'aba bakulembera
  77,39,Bwe muba mulina engeri gyemuyinza okwebulankanyamu kale munnebulankanyeko
  77,40,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa